OL,3,COfficer acted 'lawfully and
OL,4,Cnecessarily' when ramming calf with
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FA probe, into the moment an officer
OL,8,Fused his police car to ram an escaped
OL,9,Fcalf has found they acted "lawfully
OL,10,Fand necessarily."
OL,12,FFootage which investigators described
OL,13,Fas 'distressing', showed the 10-month-
OL,14,Fold calf, named Beau Lucy, hit by a
OL,15,Fpolice car twice on a residential road
OL,16,Fin Feltham, suffering grazes and
OL,17,Fbruises as a result.
