OL,3,COfficer acted 'lawfully and
OL,4,Cnecessarily' when ramming calf with
OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FThe police had said the officers were
OL,8,Fconcerned for the public's safety and
OL,9,Fhad tried to capture the calf safely
OL,10,Ffor "a number of hours".
OL,12,FIt happened on Friday, June 15 at
OL,13,Faround 8.55pm after the force received
OL,14,Freports that a cow was running loose
OL,15,Fin the streets.
OL,17,FAfter the incident the police officer
OL,18,Fwas "removed from frontline duties"
OL,19,Fwhile the force investigated but will
OL,20,Fsoon be returning to work.
