OL,7,FMany people raised concerns about the
OL,8,Ftreatment of the cow, including the
OL,9,Fthen Home Secretary James Cleverly,
OL,10,Fwho said it seemed "unnecessarily
OL,11,Fheavy handed."
OL,13,FMeanwhile wildlife presenter and
OL,14,Fconservationist Chris Packham asked:
OL,15,F"What sort of monster rams a calf?"
OL,17,FThe owner of the calf has described
OL,18,Fthe incident as "horrific".
