OL,7,FRob, who does not wish to give his
OL,8,Fsurname, said the "method of dealing
OL,9,Fwith the situation was incorrect...it
OL,10,Fcould have been handled so much
OL,11,Fbetter".
OL,13,FThe five month Surrey Police
OL,14,Finvestigation into the incident
OL,15,Freviewed over 250 pieces of video
OL,16,Ffootage, 75 witness statements and
OL,17,Fasked animal welfare experts to
OL,18,Fdetermine if the actions of those
OL,19,Finvolved on the night amounted to the
OL,20,Foffence of causing unnecessary
OL,21,Fsuffering to the calf .
