OL,5,Cpolice car
OL,7,FA Sussex Police Senior Investigating
OL,8,FOfficer said that while footage of the
OL,9,Fincident was distressing in nature,
OL,10,Fthose involved in the incident acted
OL,11,Fwithin their duties.
OL,13,FThey added, the tactics adopted were
OL,14,Fboth lawful and necessary to prevent
OL,15,Fharm to the public and property, so no
OL,16,Ffurther action will be taken in either
OL,17,Fthe criminal investigation, or the
OL,18,Finternal misconduct matter.
