OL,7,FDeputy Chief Constable, Nev Kemp,
OL,8,Fsaid; "We appreciate the strength of
OL,9,Ffeeling which remains in relation to
OL,10,Fthis incident, which is why we
OL,11,Fcommitted to conducting a diligent and
OL,12,Fthorough investigation to determine
OL,13,Fwhether any criminal offences had
OL,14,Ftaken place in relation to the actions
OL,15,Ftaken by Surrey Police on the night.
OL,17,FCharlie Frost reports from the scene,
OL,18,Fthe day after the incident happened
