OL,7,F"This incident has highlighted several
OL,8,Fissues in relation to how the police
OL,9,Frespond to a loose livestock incident
OL,10,Fand therefore, as a Force, we want to
OL,11,Fdo what we can to reduce the
OL,12,Fpossibility of any event like this
OL,13,Fhappening again, not just in Surrey
OL,14,Fbut anywhere in the country. We have
OL,15,Freviewed the recommendations made by
OL,16,Fthe SIO and experts in this area, and
OL,17,Fwill be working to address these
OL,18,Fpromptly, sharing any best practice
OL,19,Fwith Forces across the UK.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
