OL,7,F"We have already made changes to our
OL,8,Fprotocol for loose livestock. These
OL,9,Fchanges were developed in partnership
OL,10,Fwith a new national advice working
OL,11,Fgroup, which we established following
OL,12,Fthe incident, to seek guidance from
OL,13,Fexperts including the British Animal
OL,14,FRescue and Trauma Care Association,
OL,15,FBritish Cattle Veterinary Association,
OL,16,FNational Farmers Union, and the
OL,17,FNational Rural Crime Unit. I am
OL,18,Fgrateful to them for their support and
OL,19,Fguidance."
